J‘ to questions I ask? J‘

40:29.010 --> 40:33.344
J‘ My paper heart
has been burning J‘

40:33.473 --> 40:35.464
- Hey.

40:35.600 --> 40:37.215
- Hey.

40:37.352 --> 40:39.468
- So I talked to Vince and Dave
down at The Herald

40:39.604 --> 40:41.265
and they're gonna make sure
that the town

40:41.397 --> 40:43.353
knows the truth
about what happened.

40:43.483 --> 40:45.439
I think it's gonna make it
a lot easier

40:45.568 --> 40:46.978
for your family to stay.

40:47.111 --> 40:49.944
I'm glad you're able
to keep your home.

40:50.073 --> 40:51.188
- Hmm.

40:51.324 --> 40:53.189
Last couple of days
couldn't make me leave.

40:53.326 --> 40:54.486
Forget about it.

40:54.619 --> 40:55.825
- Yeah.

40:55.954 --> 40:58.195
- Audrey,
I need to ask you something.

40:58.331 --> 40:59.821
- Sure.

40:59.958 --> 41:03.166
- I've been there
in my house

41:03.294 --> 41:07.958
with James for a year.

41:08.091 --> 41:11.834
But I never touched him,

41:11.970 --> 41:15.428
never felt him.

41:15.556 --> 41:17.968
How come you can?

41:22.271 --> 41:24.353
- I don't know.

41:29.821 --> 41:32.528
- You know, if this
is your family business,

41:32.657 --> 41:36.650
you're doing pretty good.

41:36.786 --> 41:39.152
I think Lucy would be proud.

41:43.334 --> 41:44.870
- I should go.

41:45.003 --> 41:47.119
[chuckling]
- See you around.

41:47.255 --> 41:55.253
