41:58.391 --> 42:02.225
[indistinct chatter]

42:02.353 --> 42:03.559
- You think I'm bluffing
the call?

42:03.688 --> 42:05.644
- All righty.
Here we go.

42:05.773 --> 42:10.392
- J‘ I never was someone
who knew what to say J‘

42:10.528 --> 42:15.192
